│ I will use the `sed` command with output redirection to a temporary file, followed by `mv` to replace the original file.     │
│ This method is robust. Immediately after the file is replaced, I will call `submit-patch` using the `&&` operator. This      │
│ ensures that `submit-patch` only runs if the file modification was successful.                                               │
│                                                                                                                              │
│ The patch itself remains the same: I will add a check at the beginning of the `foldShuffleToIdentity` function in            │
│ `llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/VectorCombine.cpp` to return early if a `shufflevector` operand is a `CallInst` with operand  │
│ bundles, thus avoiding the crash.                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                              │
│ ```bash                                                                                                                      │
│ sed '/auto \*SI = dyn_cast<ShuffleVectorInst>(&I);/a \                                                                       │
│   if (auto *CI = dyn_cast<CallInst>(I.getOperand(0))) \                                                                      │
│     if (CI->hasOperandBundles()) \                                                                                           │
│       return false; \                                                                                                        │
│   if (auto *CI = dyn_cast<CallInst>(I.getOperand(1))) \                                                                      │
│     if (CI->hasOperandBundles()) \                                                                                           │
│       return false;' llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/VectorCombine.cpp > VectorCombine.cpp.tmp && mv VectorCombine.cpp.tmp     │
│ llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/VectorCombine.cpp && submit-patch                                                              │
│ ```                                                                                                                          │
